{"tid":735350,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"中國足協討論讓中國國足打中超","createTime":"2018-07-09T11:53:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-10T04:45:10.000Z","uid":135753,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"ba8512dde194fbbfa86095853a99790f72b18f47","tid":735350,"uid":135753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T11:53:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> 記者：足協討論讓國足打中超</span></span><br />\n<br />\n足球記者馬德興在微博上表示，中國足協正在討論讓國足打中超的計劃。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馬德興寫道：&ldquo;此時此刻，我們偉大的中國足協正在北京展開會議，討論中國足球復興的偉大計劃。其核心之一內容就是：中國國家隊參加中超聯賽！多麼偉大的人做偉大的事。作為一名跑了快30年的老傢伙，看到國家隊打中超的計劃，感覺偉大的中國足協終於領悟了！這是多麼痛的領悟啊！這個決定真是太好了，太偉大了，太英明了！我舉三隻手贊成與歡迎。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n記者趙宇也在微博上透露：&ldquo;是的，確實在討論。也要搞什麼A隊、B隊計劃，但我覺得應該通不過吧。要是通過了，豈不是被全世界笑話？首先全世界都沒這麼幹的。另外也沒有任何可行性。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"333c17db07ec68d76fd2d01fc7211a1701ea55a6","tid":735350,"uid":155079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T11:58:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 偉大嘅智障"},{"pid":"b195a30e722ad637fa71817547218d53c3c03709","tid":735350,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T12:00:18.000Z","msg":"中國邏輯？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5286d7f8d58711b2112d517a6a2b8d7726da950d","tid":735350,"uid":84013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T12:03:26.000Z","msg":"踢完第一年就降班<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c97f28c4ec37daae55b9604055db5f2bfe82ccd","tid":735350,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-09T12:04:00.000Z","msg":"個腦究竟裝咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.